function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	idLeyranaFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(ID_LEYRANA_FOLLOWER)
	id_Self = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idLeyranaFollower) then
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(idLeyranaFollower)
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idLeyranaFollower, false)
		Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(CONVO_Wait, id_Self, idLeyranaFollower)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idLeyranaFollower, ID_LEYRANA_PreDRLG, "NPC_RUN", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idLeyranaFollower, ID_LEYRANA_PreDRLG)
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idLeyranaFollower)
		Hydra.ActorDelete(idLeyranaFollower)
	end
	
end

function Start()

	-- Set Ghost var if it exists, else spawn it 
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(id_Ghost) then
		id_Ghost = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_RogueInnerSight_Akara")[1]	
	else
		for id, i in ipairs(Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_RogueInnerSight_BakiraAll")) do
			Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(i)
		end
		id_Ghost = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_RogueInnerSight_Akara")[1]
	end

	id_CorpseChest = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_RogueInnerSight_BakiraCorpse")[1]
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(id_CorpseChest) then
		-- Disable corpse sign
		Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(id_CorpseChest, true)
	end
	-- Ghost to Hostile
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(id_Ghost) then
		Hydra.QActorStopAllQueuedActions(id_Ghost)
		Hydra.ActorAIOverrideNormalBehavior(id_Ghost, "NPC_Combat_Melee_BAsic")
		Hydra.ActorSetAIBehavior(id_Ghost, Hydra.AIBEHAVIOR_TYPE_NORMAL)
		Hydra.ActorSetTeam(id_Ghost, Hydra.TEAM_MONSTER_0)
		Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(id_Ghost, false)
		Hydra.ActorSetAIState(id_Ghost, "aggressive")
	end
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, sWorldName)

	-- Ping Ghost Spawner
	for id, i in ipairs(Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_RogueInnerSight_BakiraAll")) do
		Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(i)
	end
	
	id_Ghost = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_RogueInnerSight_Akara")[1]
	-- Ghost to Hostile
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(id_Ghost) then
		Hydra.QActorStopAllQueuedActions(id_Ghost)
		Hydra.ActorAIOverrideNormalBehavior(id_Ghost, "NPC_Combat_Melee_BAsic")
		Hydra.ActorSetAIBehavior(id_Ghost, Hydra.AIBEHAVIOR_TYPE_NORMAL)
		Hydra.ActorSetTeam(id_Ghost, Hydra.TEAM_MONSTER_0)
		Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(id_Ghost, false)
		Hydra.ActorSetAIState(id_Ghost, "aggressive")
	end

	-- Disable Corpse Sign
	id_CorpseChest = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_RogueInnerSight_BakiraCorpse")[1]
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(id_CorpseChest) then
		Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(id_CorpseChest, true)
	end
end
	
end

	--[[

	end
	]]
